A-Skip-1.exAct: Smoothly drive alternating knees and toes up in rhythmic fashion
A-Skip-1.exStart: Good posture, split arms, quickly pull knee and toe to chest while pushing opposing heel backwards.

Acceleration Build Runs-1.exAct: Run forward, gradually build speed during required distance

Carioca to Sprint-1.exAct: Lateral leg shuffle, after 3 crossover steps rotate 90 degrees and sprint

Heel Raise-1.exAct: Alternate knees and heels up AFAP

Hip Bridge-1.exStart: Start lying on back with knees bent, feet planted on the ground

Jerk-1.exAct: In one explosive movement, extend barbell overhead while dropping one foot behind the body.

Moving Plank-1.exStart: From pushup position, Keeping core stiff

Overhead Press-1.exAct: Press bar up extending arms overhead

Partner-resisted Lateral Lunge-1.exStart: Partner standing to the side of played

Partner-resisted Squat-1.exStart: Partner standing to side of player.

Plank-1.exStart: Start with forearms and toes touching the ground

Power Skip-1.exAct: Skip with large vertical jump.  Skipping remains rhythmic and smooth

Pushup-1.exAct: Lower body down, push back up with stiff core

Reverse Crab Walk-1.exAct: Keeping hips elevated, push from heels, stabilize with arms, moving backwards
Reverse Crab Walk-1.exStart: feet and palms planted on ground, fingers pointed backwards, hips elevated and pointed skyward

Reverse Walking Lunges with ball-1.exAct: Reach one foot backwards, flex front knee to 90 degrees, push off front foot back to standing
Reverse Walking Lunges with ball-1.exStart: Stand with good posture holding soccer ball overhead with straight arms

Scap Dip-1.exStart: Straight arms planted on bench, hips elevated body in a straight line

Scap Pushup-1.exAct: Lower body level by slouching shoulders keep body straight. Push body up from shoulders

Shoulder tap-planks -1.exStart: From pushup position, Keeping core stiff

Shoulder-Extension Plank-1.exStart: From pushup position, Keeping core stiff

Side Plank-1.exAct: Hold body in straight-line, core stiff

Single Leg Hip Bridge-1.exAct: Drive hips up from planted heel, squeeze glutes

Split Squat-1.exAct: In lunge position, one leg elevated backwards on bench
